snippet.title: VR support for I Can Gun
snippet.description:
Massive update for "I Can Gun". Introducing VR support and a lot of other improvements.

Download on itch.io: https://patrickkoenig.itch.io/i-can-gun

Please share your experience. Also feel free to join the Discord server to participate in the further development: https://discordapp.com/invite/ekqXSrm
